This is a great opportunity to build my vulnerability skills. I have been wanting to do this for a while. I need to write my narrative maybe. Holding everything so close to the vest is really bad for me. Use this as an opportunity to open up to people I like. People want to help. 

The hard part will be all the pepole I don’t want to deal with. at work will be tough for me. But that’s such a small price to pay for such a great opportunity. It’s so hard for me to say “I’m worried my wife will leave me, can we hang out” but it’s easy to say “I lost my job and am trying to find a new one. can we hang out?” This is such an opportunity to build friendships. Everything has a price and a little discomfort with Adam or Monica is a small price to pay.
